snippet.title: Life is full of surprises and funny moments that make you laugh - Funny compilation
snippet.description:
Here's a video clip collection of funny moments from all over the World! I'm sure all these animals (dogs, puppies, cats, kittens, raccoons, geese), kids, babies, toddlers and other people with their fails will make you laugh pretty hard! Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

WANT TO SEE YOUR PET IN OUR COMPILATIONS?
Send your clips or links to: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/tigerstudiosfun
